---
title: Seared Chicken & Katsu Sauce with Sweetcorn Rice & Creamy Slaw
description: Let’s introduce the star of tonight’s dinner, katsu sauce, perfect for drizzling over these golden and seared chicken bites and soaking into the popping sweetcorn rice.
